<p><strong>Notes: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Rich Content Editor includes a word count display below the bottom right corner of the text box.</li>
<li>Math equations must be added using the <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-math-Equation-Editor-in-the-Rich-Content-Editor/ta-p/377" target="_blank">Math Editor</a> in the Rich Content Editor.</li>
</ul>
